Please Read, Taylor💕

I know I’m an introvert. Using social media too much exhausts me mentally. I need to take breaks frequently. But even during these periods of inactivity online, I never stop defending, supporting and celebrating you, Taylor.

I know I’m not the most creative, funniest, out-going person out there. But these are NOT FLAWS. I’m awesoME the way I am. Taylor, thanks for helping me see that. You helped me embrace my individuality, and released “Me!” at the right moment, at the right time. Your music is my HOME. 💕💕💕 @taylorswift
